49
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:26,010
♪Deeply trapped
in a vortex of mysteries♪

50
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:29,590
♪Wading through
the muddy waters of hearts and times♪

51
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:33,529
